Awesome‚Äîhere‚Äôs a clean, Ansible 2.9‚Äìcompatible version of the venafi_cert_renew role with all the key files and fixes we‚Äôve been iterating on (global dict consolidation, robust backup/restore without ‚Äúno last item‚Äù, Outlook‚Äëfriendly reports, dry‚Äërun mode, etc.). I‚Äôll show:

The role layout

Every YAML you need under tasks/

defaults/, vars/, and handlers/

The two HTML templates

A sample dry‚Äërun playbook

I‚Äôve kept comments concise so you can drop this straight into a repo.

Role layout
roles/
‚îî‚îÄ venafi_cert_renew/
   ‚îú‚îÄ defaults/
   ‚îÇ  ‚îî‚îÄ main.yml
   ‚îú‚îÄ vars/
   ‚îÇ  ‚îî‚îÄ main.yml
   ‚îú‚îÄ handlers/
   ‚îÇ  ‚îî‚îÄ main.yml
   ‚îú‚îÄ templates/
   ‚îÇ  ‚îú‚îÄ report_full.html.j2
   ‚îÇ  ‚îî‚îÄ report_dry.html.j2
   ‚îî‚îÄ tasks/
      ‚îú‚îÄ main.yml
      ‚îú‚îÄ download_vcert.yml
      ‚îú‚îÄ fetch_pems.yml
